<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Connect Your Charles Schwab Account</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00a0dc 0%, #0077c8 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #00a0dc;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 15px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .info-section h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            padding: 12px 0;
            padding-left: 32px;
            position: relative;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .feature-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #48bb78;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .security-badge {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .security-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .security-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .security-text strong {
            display: block;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .security-text span {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00a0dc 0%, #0077c8 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 119, 200, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            color: #a0aec0;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer-note a {
            color: #0077c8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-note a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .info-section h2 {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .feature-list li {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">CS</div>
            <h1>Connect Your Schwab Account</h1>
            <p>Securely link your Charles Schwab account to continue</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="security-badge">
                <div class="security-icon">ðŸ”’</div>
                <div class="security-text">
                    <strong>Bank-level security</strong>
                    <span>Your credentials are encrypted and never stored</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/u/login/schwab" class="btn-primary">
                Connect to Charles Schwab
            </a>

            <p class="footer-note">
                You can disconnect at any time by following <a href="https://www.schwab.com/content/how-to-manage-third-party-access-to-my-account-information">these steps</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>